  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, coming to this Austria, to Linz, Austria, they ask me I should become an active member in a political organization Betar, Zionist organizations.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before the party was in existence, and as a matter of fact, most of the Jewish parties, political parties, were in existence when I came over there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, I said, I agreed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, if I'll see that it will fit for my-- for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Willingly or unwillingly I became very active over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I became chairman of the organization over there in Linz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I was also a member of the central committee of our organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that time they organized also a Congress of the Jewish people in Austria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I became, of course, a delegate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was talking over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were organizing the people in Austria, the, the displaced people, the Jewish people in Austria.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people started to come in more involved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But, but what we didn't expect-- let me first, I became very active.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I became also a member of the Federation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I became Vice President of the Federation of the Zionist organizations in Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were-- I had to go and visit the various camps, this-- the DP camps, they called them, and organize people who were willing to go illegally with Aliyah Bet to Palestine that time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well, this was a very rewarding job that I had, and very prestigious job that I had at time over there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then after a while, I decided that it's not just that we have to work for somebody to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I decided with my sister and her boyfriend that we will go with the illegal, this organization, we'll go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we organized.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
